ip_address":"","ucode":"4A8120C4AA6F2F","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/11/6c/f9/af80b4da.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1527915235,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"5822882531","product_id":100002401,"comment_content":"我优先的心态 是自我感觉良好 实际上自己认为的和实际情况相去甚远","like_count":1},{"had_liked":false,"id":4307,"user_name":"冰狼","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1064817,"ip_address":"","ucode":"F41714B1AE20A7","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/10/3f/71/35077482.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1521965659,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"5816932955","product_id":100002401,"comment_content":"其实作为一个管理者的同时也是作为一个下属，有分配任务的职责也有领受任务的职责。在分配任务的时候可以基于任务的特点进行分配，而在领受任务的时候可以加入自己的理解来考虑如何高效执行，领导需要的是能理解着执行任务的员工","like_count":1},{"had_liked":false,"id":968,"user_name":"huangzhimim","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1018596,"ip_address":"","ucode":"ACAB00327DD95D","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/0f/8a/e4/e5e1fd9b.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1511784440,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"5806751736","product_id":100002401,"comment_content":"像“上次就搞砸了”这种言论很打击组员的信心，管理者应该鼓励成员多去尝试和独立解决问题，作为成员也要避免同样的问题再次发生并且举一反三","like_count":1},{"had_liked":false,"id":859,"user_name":"JK.Ryan","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1014467,"ip_address":"","ucode":"D1E533F3DEC481","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/0f/7a/c3/abb7bfe3.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1511369599,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"5806336895","product_id":100002401,"comment_content":"写得很赞","like_count":1},{"had_liked":false,"id":851,"user_name":"大斌","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1002183,"ip_address":"","ucode":"1434C2B0A29135","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/0f/4a/c7/ec18673b.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1511351527,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"5806318823","product_id":100002401,"comment_content":"信任员工，让他放手去做，事成之后一起分析，购买必要的学习资源（书籍，培训班）","like_count":1},{"had_liked":false,"id":621,"user_name":"😺🤓😺","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1012858,"ip_address":"","ucode":"BBE313EE5AD213","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/0f/74/7a/0dfb43f4.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1511145509,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"5806112805","product_id":100002401,"comment_content":"根据事情结果对相关人员进行引导并反馈，再次确认结果并反馈… 达到预期目标","like_count":1},{"had_liked":false,"id":338635,"user_name":"怀揣梦想的学渣","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1916685,"ip_address":"","ucode":"2349B9F4F6FDE3","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/1d/3f/0d/1e8dbb2c.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1647611410,"is_pvip":true,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1647611410","product_id":100002401,"comment_content":"看完文章，真实有收获到如何向下更优质的管理，而非局限于向下管理。<br>翻了一下其他评论，又收获了一些实践经验的分享，看到这篇文章晚了几年，但还是有真实的收获。<br>看来赵成推荐的是值得看。","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":331425,"user_name":"尹子昊","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1214174,"ip_address":"","ucode":"C73906E8FDE167","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/12/86/de/ef145965.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1642582175,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1642582175","product_id":100002401,"comment_content":"对于新同事，我一般是先带着一起做一个中小型项目，过程带着了解梳理业务，设计方案，同时也会在过程中了解新同事的一个风格类型，例如：是对技术钻研得很深还是在沟通协调方面比较擅长，这样有利于后期的任务针对性安排。<br>上级这块对我辅导主要体现在两种风格，一种是技术方案会过得很细，会问你为什么这样设计，还有没有更好的方式呢？或者是文档要写得清楚，让大家能很容易看懂。这种会让我在细节把控方面成长很快。<br>另一种主要是放手信任你去做，包括方案设计、资源分配的决策，他会在过程中问下你的情况，有没有需要帮助的，这种会让我从点到面的成长，提升做事格局，因为过程中自己要做抉择，部门内外资源协调等。","like_count":1},{"had_liked":false,"id":304053,"user_name":"杨明","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1069970,"ip_address":"","ucode":"D